  <h3><u>Img Tag</u></h3>
                <ul type="Square">
                    <li>In HTML, images are inserted using < img > tag.</li>
                    <li>The < img > tag is an empty tag.</li>
                    <li>There are three types of image files which can be used in HTML, indicated by different file name extensions: .jpg, .gif and .png.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>The img element has a number of attributes:</p>
                    <h3><u>Required Attributes Img Tag</u></h3>
            <table bordercolor="DarkOrange" border="3">
                   <tr bgcolor="DarkOrchid"> 
                        <th>Attribute</th>
                        <th>Description</th>

                        <th>Possible values</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr bgcolor="DarkOrchid"> 
                        <td>src</td>
                        <td>The location/path of the image files to be inserted on the webpage</td>

                        <td>URL</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr bgcolor="DarkOrchid"> 
                        <td>alt</td>
                        <td>Text</td>
                        <td>Specifies alternate text</td>
                    </tr>
            </table>
                                <h3><u>Optional Attributes Img Tag</u></h3>            
            <table bordercolor="DarkSalmon" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" border="1" height="30%" width="90%">
                    <tr bgcolor="DarkSlateBlue"> 
                                <th>Attribute</th>
                                <th>Value</th>
                                <th>Description</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr bgcolor="DarkSlateBlue"> 
                                <td>Aling</td>
                                <td>Top<br>
                                    Bottom<br>
                                    Middle<br>
                                    Left<br>
                                    Right<br>
                                </td>
                                <td>Specifies the alingment fo the image.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr bgcolor="DarkSlateBlue">
                        <td>Border</td>
                        <td>Pixels</td>
                        <td>Specifies the width of the image border.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr bgcolor="DarkSlateBlue">
                        <td>Height</td>
                        <td>Pixels or %</td>
                        <td>Specifies the height of the image border.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr bgcolor="DarkSlateBlue">
                        <td>Width</td>
                        <td>Pixels or %</td>
                        <td>Sets the width of an image.</td>
                    </tr>
            </table>
            
